Dialogue.Speaker: Uhc Eclipse information line
Dialogue.Speech: Thank you for calling Uhc Eclipse information line. This is How may help you?

Dialogue.Speaker: Caller
Dialogue.Speech: I'm calling about your new cigarette. I want to find out more about it for free.

Dialogue.Speaker: Uhc Eclipse information line
Dialogue.Speech: I'll be happy to help you, ma'am/sir, but first may I have your zip code please?

Dialogue.Speaker: Uhc Eclipse information line
Dialogue.Speech: May I have your home phone number please?

Dialogue.Speaker: Uhc Eclipse information line
Dialogue.Speech: We can talk with non-smokers over the age of 21 and give out limited information; however, you cannot participate in any of our promotions. If you'd like, we have a brochure of information that we can send you.

Dialogue.Speaker: Uhc Eclipse information line
Dialogue.Speech: Thank you for your interest. You should be receiving this information within 2-3 weeks. May I have your date of birth please?

Dialogue.Speaker: Uhc Eclipse information line
Dialogue.Speech: Mr/Ms. [tobacco company], We want to ensure that we don't mail or talk to individuals under the age of 21. So, I'm sure you can understand why we'd like to know your date of birth.
